article.description: — Joe Quintana had 24 points as Loyola Marymount got past SMU 76-70 on Monday night.
article.headline: Quintana scores 24 to lift Loyola Marymount over SMU 76-70
article.linkText: Quintana scores 24 to lift Loyola Marymount over SMU 76-70
article.story: JACKSONVILLE, Fla. -- — Joe Quintana had 24 points as Loyola Marymount got past SMU 76-70 on Monday night. Eli Scott had 18 points for Loyola Marymount (3-2). Keli Leaupepe added 11 points. Dameane Douglas had 10 points. Kendric Davis had 17 points for the Mustangs (3-3). Zach Nutall added 15 points. Jahmar Young Jr. had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
